Frank Gatliff https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Frank_Gatliff 0 Frank Ernest Gatliff (1927–1990) was an Australian actor based in Great Britain, in several films but mostly on TV, in such series as Gideon's Way, The Baron, Danger Man, The Avengers, Department S, Strange Report, The Persuaders!, Doctor Who (in the serial The Monster of Peladon), Rising Damp, The Good Life, The Onedin Line, Blake's 7, Minder and C.A.B..
